gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Raptors 121, Bulls 108
gameRecap.excerpt: OG Anunoby went 10-14 from the floor for 26 points along with six rebounds, and three assists as the Raptors defeated the Bulls, 121-108. Pascal Siakam added 18 points and eight assists while Scottie Barnes tallied 13 points, 10 rebounds, and six assists in the win. Zach LaVine led the Bulls with 36 points, four rebounds, and three assists in the loss. The Raptors improve to 8-8 on the year and 1-2 in East C play as the Bulls move to 5-12 and 0-3 in East C play. The Bulls have been eliminated from the In-Season Tournament Knockout Round with the loss. Despite the win tonight, Toronto was eliminated with the Orlando victory earlier today.
